description: Traack Technologies Inc. provides business and finance advisory services for small and medium sized companies. The company focuses on creating business plans and general management consulting. Its advisory services include corporate formation and structure, business plan creation and development, business planning and expansion, strategic planning, mergers and acquisition, and business advisory services. The company was formerly known as Nvest Inc. and changed its name to Traack Technologies Inc. in July 2021. The company is based in Bellevue, Washington.
